WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:03.100
The emperor and the girl Moxi ask to see you

2
00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:07.900
Yue Fei is back, he saved your life

3
00:00:07.900 --> 00:00:09.133
Is there any reason not to see?

4
00:00:09.133 --> 00:00:10.966
Dove, bring him in

5
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:15.533
The emperor's ministers have a hard time

6
00:00:15.533 --> 00:00:17.266
What are you wronged about?

7
00:00:17.266 --> 00:00:18.566
I will give you justice

8
00:00:18.566 --> 00:00:21.766
Emperor Xiao Huang wants you to inherit the throne

9
00:00:21.766 --> 00:00:24.900
Intentionally marrying the courtiers and daughters to the bitter and cold land of the northwest

10
00:00:24.900 --> 00:00:25.966
There is such a thing

11
00:00:25.966 --> 00:00:27.166
Why don't I know

12
00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:29.566
Xiao Huang is just to keep you from being distracted

13
00:00:29.766 --> 00:00:31.166
Nature won't let you know

14
00:00:31.166 --> 00:00:33.766
Your Majesty, look at this woman's hands

15
00:00:33.766 --> 00:00:35.733
I've been tortured beyond recognition

16
00:00:35.733 --> 00:00:37.633
I finally escaped

17
00:00:37.666 --> 00:00:39.400
I don't want any glory and wealth

18
00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:41.733
I just want the emperor to feed me

19
00:00:41.733 --> 00:00:43.366
Leave me in the palace

20
00:00:45.866 --> 00:00:47.200
Since you have a favor with the emperor

21
00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:48.800
Naturally, there is no reason not to leave you behind.

22
00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:50.000
You can stay in the palace

23
00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:51.200
Thank you, madam

24
00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:52.400
Thank you, Your Majesty

25
00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:53.700
courtiers retire

